    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like growth though. it just feels like i'm a burden. every time i try to fix things, i just make it worse for them. i look at them and i just see how much easier their lives would be if they didn't have to deal with my shit. it's like i'm just a shadow hanging over them.",
